"guidebook.chapter.COT.DruidicsProfessions": "[center][font=dialogue]Professions[/font][/center]
  
Like vanilla skills, the Druidics skill provides professions that change the gameplay experience at levels 5 and 10.
 
[font=dialogue]Level 5[/font]
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/skilledshapeshifter.png:0,0,16,16] [color=MediumBlue]Skilled Shapeshifter[/color]
    Adds stamina regeneration ability to
    shapeshifting. Occurs after not moving
    for a few seconds.
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/ancientagronomist.png:0,0,16,16] [color=MediumBlue]Ancient Agronomist[/color]
    Reduces cost of creating ancient
    druidic seeds by one essence.
 
[font=dialogue]Level 10[/font]
[color=MediumBlue]Skilled Shapeshifter Track[/color]
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/stagpath.png:0,0,16,16] [color=blue]Stag's Path[/color] 
    Adds health regeneration to stamina
    regeneration with double the speed.
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/wolfpath.png:0,0,16,16] [color=blue]Wolf's Path[/color] 
    Adds ability to fight while shapeshifted,
    as well as a defense and attack buff. 
    Unlocks the [texttooltip=Shapeshift (Wolf):Transform into a wolf, giving a speed boost and a buff to your foraging skill. 
Also gains combat abilities.][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/wolfpath.png:0,0,16,16] [color=purple]Shapeshift (Wolf)[/color][/texttooltip] ability.
    (Usable with the [link=Title/Mechanics]Adventure Bar[/link])
 
[color=MediumBlue]Ancient Agronomist Track[/color]
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/branchofmidgard.png:0,0,16,16] [color=blue]Branch of Midgard[/color]
    All ancient crops grow 10% faster, and
    all artisan goods derived from them are
    worth 10% more. 
    > Stacks with Artisan and Agriculturist.
= [icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/druidics/branchofyggdrasil.png:0,0,16,16] [color=blue]Branch of Yggdrasil[/color]
     Druidic essences have an additional 10%
     chance to drop. Druidic crops water 
     surrounding crops with the same range 
     as a Quality Sprinkler.",

