"guidebook.chapter.UP.BardicsSkill": "[center][font=dialogue]Bardics[/font][/center]
[offset=200,0][image=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/bardics/icon.png:0,0,10,10:4]You've unlocked the Bardics skill! Bardics can be leveled up by talking to NPCs and performing songs from your [link=Title/Mechanics]Adventure Bar[/link]. 
 
Each level, you gain 10 max Aether and a new song for the adventure bar. These songs cast various effects, hover for more details.
 
[font=dialogue]Unlocks[/font]
> Level 1 - Unlocks [texttooltip=Fantasia Alla Marcia:Grants a random passive buff. 
 
> Usable once per day
> Aether cost: 20
][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:32,0,16,16][color=purple]Fantasia Alla Marcia[/color][/texttooltip].
> Level 2 - Unlocks [texttooltip=Battlefield Overture:Grants either an attack or defense buff.
 
> Usable once per day
> Aether cost: 20
 ][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:48,0,16,16][color=purple]Battlefield Overture[/color][/texttooltip].
> Level 3 - Unlocks [texttooltip=Invigorating Encore:Restores 25% health and energy.
 
> Usable once per day
> Aether cost: 10
 ][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:64,0,16,16][color=purple]Invigorating Encore[/color][/texttooltip].
> Level 4 - Unlocks [texttooltip=Enduring Melody:Creates a protective sound barrier that
keeps enemies away for 30 seconds.
 
> Unlimited daily use
> Aether cost: 10
 ][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:80,0,16,16][color=purple]Enduring Melody[/color][/texttooltip].
> Level 5 - Unlocks one of two songs based on your [link=UP/BardicsProfessions]profession[/link] choice:
 
  = College of Eloquence - [texttooltip=Rogues' Humorsque:Offers a buff depending on who it's played to.
 
> Usable once per day
> Aether cost: 25
 ][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:96,0,16,16][color=purple]Rogues' Humorsque[/color][/texttooltip]
  = College of Valor - [texttooltip=Scherzo D'Inganno:Lets out a discordant sound that
damages all enemies in range.
 
> Unlimited daily use
> Aether cost: 20
][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:112,0,16,16][color=purple]Scherzo D'Inganno[/color][/texttooltip]
 
> Level 6 - Unlocks [texttooltip=Ballad of Chronomancy:Pauses time for two minutes.

> Unlimited daily use
> Aether cost: 35
 ][icon=SMAPI/kcc.sns/assets/abilities.png:0,16,16,16][color=purple]Ballad of Chronomancy[/color][/texttooltip].
