"guidebook.chapter.TOP.Intro": "[center][font=dialogue]Chapter 4[/font][/center]
[center][font=dialogue]The Other Promise[/font][/center]
   
The forth chapter of S&S revolves around a quest to rescue Dandelion, the heroic partner of questionable Sorcerer, Roslin, her and her patron, Solomon. Uncover the secrets of the Arcane, master the use of Elemental Essences, become a Sorcerer yourself, become an Alchemist, become a Paladin (if you aren't already) and lay waste to the haunted beast hidden in the Deep Dark underneath The Scarp. ",

"guidebook.chapter.TOP.Roslin": "[nospacing]
[nextposition=0,10][center=300][font=dialogue]Roslin[/font][/center]
[offset=118,50][image=Characters/Roslin:0,0,16,32:4]
[offset=-118,144][center=300]Pronouns: She/Her[/center]
[offset=0,32][center=300]Birthday: Spring 26[/center]
[nextposition=322,16][image=Portraits/Roslin:0,0,64,64:4]
[nextposition=0,288]
[/nospacing]
Roslin is a skilled Sorcerer hailing from the city of Amon'Zod, a desert city a continent away. Her deal with the Shadowfolk, Solomon, has bolstered her elemental Mastery beyond what most mortals are able to achieve.",

"guidebook.chapter.TOP.Dandelion": "[nospacing]
[nextposition=0,10][center=300][font=dialogue]Dandelion[/font][/center]
[offset=118,50][image=Characters/Dandelion:0,0,16,32:4]
[offset=-118,144][center=300]Pronouns: She/Her[/center]
[offset=0,32][center=300]Birthday: Summer 16[/center]
[nextposition=322,16][image=Portraits/Dandelion:0,0,64,64:4]
[nextposition=0,288]
[/nospacing]
Dandelion is a Paladin who's got a tumultuous relationship with her Oath, and apparent difficulty keeping track of her limbs. Despite her heroic tendencies, she aches to lay her sword and shield down by the flowers.",

"guidebook.chapter.TOP.Solomon": "[nospacing]
[nextposition=0,10][center=300][font=dialogue]Solomon[/font][/center]
[offset=118,50][image=Characters/Solomon:0,0,16,32:4]
[offset=-118,144][center=300]Pronouns: He/Him[/center]
[offset=0,32][center=300]Not Friendable[/center]
[nextposition=322,16][image=Portraits/Solomon:0,0,64,64:4]
[nextposition=0,288]
[/nospacing]
Solomon is annoying on a good day. Troublesome, crass, and mischevious, this Shadowfolk is an expert in the occult. He's got quite an ego about it, though, one which may not entirely be warrented. He is intrinsically connected to Roslin.",

