"guidebook.chapter.Epilogue.FinalMessage": "[center][font=dialogue]Final Message[/font][/center]
 
[image=Mods/Sword & Sorcery/InMemoryOfLoreSeeker]
    
This project is dedicated to the memory of TheLoreSeeker, a beloved community member who made a point to encourage people's wildest ideas. He may no longer be with us, but he lives on in the content of those he inspired. Thank you, to him and everyone else who contributed to S&S. And especially to you, the player, {{IsModComplete}}. Signed with love, DestyNova.",

"guidebook.chapter.DeepDark.Intro": "[center][font=dialogue]Introduction[/font][/center]
 
The Deep Dark is a late-game 30 [link=DeepDark/Floors]floor[/link] dungeon crawling with powerful [link=DeepDark/Monsters]monsters[/link] and the rare ore, [Link=DeepDark/Stygium]Stygium[/link]. Here you'll find beautiful maps, custom forage and new monsters with unique item drop pools. Once you reach the end you'll face off against the mod's final boss: The [Link=DeepDark/Duskspire]Duskspire Behemoth[/link].
 
It's advised you prepare yourself with Sword & Sorcery's new mechanics and late-game vanilla mechanics before tackling this location.",
