"guidebook.chapter.DeepDark.Stygium": "[center][font=dialogue]Stygium[/font][/center]
 
Stygium is a rare and powerful ore that spawns only within the Deep Dark. It is used to further upgrade your tools past [color=purple]Iridium[/color] tier. Be warned, the increased strength comes with a cost.
 
[font=dialogue]Stygium Resources[/font]
> [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_StygiumOreStone][icon=maps/DeepDark-rocks:144,32,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Nodes[/color][/itemtooltip] - Spawn in the Deep Dark
> [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_StygiumOre][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:0,160,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Ore[/color][/itemtooltip] - Drops from Stygium Nodes
> [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_StygiumBar][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:144,144,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Bars[/color][/itemtooltip] - Smelted from Stygium Ore
 
[font=dialogue]Stygium Gear[/font]
Stygium Tools are made by upgrading any [color=purple]Iridium[/color] tool with [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_StygiumBar][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:144,144,16,16][color=blue]Stygium Bars[/color][/itemtooltip] at Clint's. This will improve the tool as expected for the next tier.
 
Stygium Gear List
> [itemtooltip=(T)DN.SnS_StygiumPickaxe][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/StygiumTools:80,64,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Pickaxe[/color][/itemtooltip]
> [itemtooltip=(T)DN.SnS_StygiumHoe][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/StygiumTools:80,32,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Hoe[/color][/itemtooltip]
> [itemtooltip=(T)DN.SnS_StygiumAxe][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/StygiumTools:80,96,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Axe[/color][/itemtooltip]
> [itemtooltip=(T)DN.SnS_StygiumWateringCan][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/StygiumTools:48,128,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Watering Can[/color][/itemtooltip]
> [itemtooltip=(W)DN.SnS_StygiumBlade][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/StygiumTools:0,0,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Blade[/color][/itemtooltip] (Recipe: Lion's Mane)
> [itemtooltip=(W)DN.SnS_StygiumShield][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:80,192,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Shield[/color][/itemtooltip] (Recipe: Default)
> [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_StygiumArmor][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSArsenal:0,112,16,16] [color=blue]Stygium Armor[/color][/itemtooltip] (Recipe: Artificer level-up)
 
Note: Improved range for chargable tools is 5x5.
 
[font=dialogue]Stygium Poisoning[/font]
When a Stygium item is worn or held it applies a de-buff, [icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:112,192,16,16] [color=purple]Stygium Poisoning[/color]. This de-buff drops the player's defense and luck until the tool is upgraded to the [link=DeepDark/Elysium]Elysium[/link] tier.",

