"guidebook.chapter.DeepDark.Duskspire": "[center][font=dialogue]Duskspire Behemoth[/font][/center]
[offset=200,0][image=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSMonsterIcons:23,66,18,13:4]The Duskspire is the final boss at the end of the Deep Dark mine. When you initially fight the Duskspire, it is a two stage fight. The first state simulates a turn-based JRPG, while the second is an arena fight using the game's typical combat mechanics.
 
When defeated, the Duskspire drops [itemtooltip=(O)DN.SnS_DuskspireHeart][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:0,192,16,16][color=blue]Duskspire Hearts[/color][/itemtooltip], which are used to purify [Link=DeepDark/Stygium]Stygium Tools[/link]. The Duskspire can then be re-fought in a weaker form to obtain more Duskspire Hearts. This fight resets every Monday.",

