 = [itemtooltip=(W)DN.SnS_DruidShield][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:64,160,16,16] [color=blue]Druid Shield[/color][/itemtooltip] - Provides 35 Armor Points. 
 = [itemtooltip=(W)DN.SnS_BardShield][icon=Textures/DN.SnS/SnSObjects:80,160,16,16] [color=blue]Bardics Shield[/color][/itemtooltip] - Provides 35 Armor Points.
