",
"guidebook.chapter.Mechanics.DualWielding": "[font=dialogue]Dual Wielding[/font]
Sword & Sorcery introduces a dual-wielding feature, allowing you to attack with two weapons at once. To equip a weapon in your off-hand slot, open your inventory and click a button to the left of the window that looks like the following:
 
[image=spacechase0.SpaceCore/ExtraEquipmentIcon]
After that, you should see a slot labelled [color=black]Offhand[/color]. Place your desired secondary weapon in that slot. Now, whenever you swing your weapon or use your weapon ability in your hotbar, both will be used.",
"guidebook.chapter.Mechanics.Powers": "[font=dialogue]Powers[/font]
Sword & Sorcery introduces 5 new powers to the game. 2 can be aquired every playthrough, while 3 require marrying one of the mod's romance candidates.
 
